title: Ground News - Uorfi Javed Bags A Big Screen Role - IndiaWest Journal News
text: MUMBAI (IANS) – Social media sensation Uorfi Javed, who is known for her unique fashion sense, will be seen in the upcoming film ‘Love Sex Aur Dhokha 2’ which will mark her big screen debut. The premise of the film is quite relevant to the current generation, which talks about love in the era of internet and social media.
